<h1>Your friend just joined a contest 🎉</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @inviter.display_name %>,</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= @invitee.display_name %></strong> just entered their first Turf Monster contest
  using your invite link.
</p>

<% if @remaining.positive? %>
  <p>
    You&rsquo;re now <strong><%= @invitees_in_contest %>/<%= @target %></strong> of the way to
    a free contest entry token. Bring
    <strong><%= @remaining %> more friend<%= "s" if @remaining != 1 %></strong>
    who enter<%= "s" if @remaining == 1 %> a contest and we&rsquo;ll credit you one entry token.
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
    That&rsquo;s <strong><%= @invitees_in_contest %> friends</strong> who&rsquo;ve entered using
    your invite link. Your free entry token is on the way &mdash; check your account page.
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Share your invite link &rarr;".html_safe, @account_url %>
</p>

<p>Thanks for spreading the word.</p>

<p>&mdash; Turf Monster</p>
